    "20975640": {
      "title": "Morphological variation of Setaria faberii and S. viridis",
      "abstract": "Fourteen morphological characteristics ofSetaria faberii andS. viridis were investigated in wild populations and in plants grown in a greenhouse under uniform treatments. Five quantitative and one qualitative characteristic, with a difference in chromosome number, proved satisfactory for distinguishing these two species. The quantitative data are presented in tables which include the ‘t’ values.S. viridis is a diploid species (2n=18), andS. faberii is a tetraploid species (2n=36)."
